    {
        "content": "<p>question related to HAPI. I have [vaccine code:3] and [system: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/vaccine-code]\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/vaccine-code]\">http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/vaccine-code]</a>. how can I use HAPI/FHIR to get the [display] and/or the [description] using java?<br>\nthanx<br>\nZak</p>",
        "id": 168332086,
        "sender_full_name": "Zak Guler",
        "timestamp": 1560794039
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>your system should be <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/cvx\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/cvx\">http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/cvx</a> - that's the URL of the code system that defines the cvx code. the value set URL just identifies a particular selection of codes.</p>",
        "id": 168332341,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1560794189
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>once you do that.. I think you use validateCode on IWorkerContext - you should have one of those hanging around, but for cvx you'll have to set it up with access to a terminology server like <a href=\"http://tx.fhir.org\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://tx.fhir.org\">http://tx.fhir.org</a> (which is not suitable for production usage)</p>",
        "id": 168332411,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1560794265
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>see <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/terminologies.html#valuesets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/terminologies.html#valuesets\">http://hl7.org/fhir/terminologies.html#valuesets</a> for more information</p>",
        "id": 168333383,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1560794988
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>See <a href=\"http://hapifhir.io/apidocs-r4/org/hl7/fhir/r4/context/IWorkerContext.html#validateCode-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://hapifhir.io/apidocs-r4/org/hl7/fhir/r4/context/IWorkerContext.html#validateCode-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-\">http://hapifhir.io/apidocs-r4/org/hl7/fhir/r4/context/IWorkerContext.html#validateCode-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-java.lang.String-</a></p>",
        "id": 168359523,
